en I invested in IonQ in February at an</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156615862/image_2156615862.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743885-ionq-stock-still-my-preferred-quantum-computing-bet", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 18:02:10"}, {"id": "4743883", "title": "Pioneer Fund Q3 2024 Performance Analysis And Market Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688767071/image_1688767071.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A graph moving up\" data-id=\"1688767071\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688767071/image_1688767071.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688767071/image_1688767071.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688767071/image_1688767071.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688767071/image_1688767071.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688767071/image_1688767071.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688767071/image_1688767071.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688767071/image_1688767071.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688767071/image_1688767071.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Average Annual Total Returns fo