s/getty_images/164333894/image_164333894.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/164333894/image_164333894.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/164333894/image_164333894.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/164333894/image_164333894.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/164333894/image_164333894.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/164333894/image_164333894.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Walter Bibikow</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Centerspace (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CSR\" title=\"Centerspace\">CSR</a></span>) has significantly outperformed the Vanguard Real Estate ETF (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VNQ\" title=\"Vanguard Real Estate ETF\">VNQ</a>) so far in 2024, delivering a ~24% total return against the ~10% gain for the broad U.S. real estate ETF:</p> <p>I last <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718260-centerspace-increased-2024-outlook-as-occupancy-recovers\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718260-centerspace-increased-2024-outlook-as-occupancy-recovers\" target=\"_blank\">covered the shares back in August</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/164333894/image_164333894.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743881-centerspace-attractively-valued-despite-signs-of-moderating-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 17:53:03"}, {"id": "4743879", "title": "Why Palantir Could Hit $89 Soon", "descrip